<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Two-Factor Authentication Code - {{ app_name }}</title>
    <style>
        /* S-Store Email Design System */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #212529;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 6px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header {
            background-color: #0f172a;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 32px 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 32px 24px;
        }
        
        h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #212529;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        
        p {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: #212529;
        }
        
        .verification-box {
            background-color: #e0e7ff;
            border: 2px solid #1e3a8a;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 32px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .verification-code {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            letter-spacing: 0.25em;
            font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, "SF Mono", Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
            margin: 16px 0;
            display: block;
        }
        
        .verification-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .security-notice {
            background-color: #fee2e2;
            border: 1px solid #dc2626;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 12px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #7f1d1d;
        }
        
        .expiry-notice {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border: 1px solid #d97706;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 12px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #78350f;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #dee2e6;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        
        .text-muted {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 24px 16px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 24px 16px;
            }
            
            .footer {
                padding: 16px;
            }
            
            .verification-code {
                font-size: 24px;
                letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1 class="logo">{{ app_name }}</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Your Two-Factor Authentication Code</h2>
            
            <p>Hi {{ user_name }},</p>
            
            <p>You've requested to sign in to your {{ app_name }} account. To complete your login, please use the verification code below:</p>
            
            <div class="verification-box">
                <div class="verification-label">Your Authentication Code</div>
                <span class="verification-code">{{ verification_code }}</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="expiry-notice">
                ‚è∞ <strong>Important:</strong> This code expires in {{ expiry_minutes }} minutes.
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-notice">
                üîí <strong>Security Notice:</strong> If you didn't request this code, someone may be trying to access your account. Please secure your account immediately by changing your password.
            </div>
            
            <div class="divider"></div>
            
            <p class="text-muted">This code was requested at {{ request_time }} from IP address {{ ip_address }}.</p>
            
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Best regards,<br><strong>The {{ app_name }} Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{ current_year }} {{ app_name }}. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
